\c 5
\s Kupindura kwechikomba
\p
\v 1 Ndapinda mumunda mangu, hanzvadzi yangu, mwenga wangu; Ndaunganidza mura yangu nezvinonhuwira zvangu; Ndadya musvi wouchi hwangu nouchi hwangu; Ndanwa waini yangu nomukaka wangu. Idyai, shamwari dzangu;
\s Inwai, zvirokwazvo, inwai zvikuru, vadiwa vangu.
\s Vaparadzana chinguva, mwenga
\s anotsvaka chikomba
\p
\v 2 Ndakanga ndivete, asi mwoyo wangu wakanga wakasvinura; Izwi romudiwa wangu,
\s anogogodza, achiti,
\s "Ndizarurire, hanzvadzi yangu, mudiwa
\s wangu, njiva yangu, akakwana wangu;
\s Nokuti musoro wangu uzere nedova,
\s Vhudzi rangu namadonhedza ousiku."
\p
\v 3 Ndabvisa nguo yangu; ndingaifuka sei?
\s Ndashambidza tsoka dzangu; ndingadzisvibisa sei?
\p
\v 4 Mudiwa watigu akapinza ruoko rwake napavhuri romukova, Mwoyo wangu ukamushuva.
\p
\v 5 Ndakasimuka, ndichiti ndizarurire mudiwa wangu;
\s Maoko angu akadonha mura, Neminwe yangu mura inoyerera, Pazvibato zvechizarira.
\p
\v 6 Ndakazarurira mudiwa wangu; Asi mudiwa wangu akanga atendeuka, aenda.
\s Mweya wangu akanga watorwa pakutaura kwake;
\s Nakamutsvaka, asi handina kumuwana;
\s Ndikamudana, asi haana kundipindura.
\p
\v 7 Varindi, vanofamba-famba neguta, vakandiwana;
\s Vakandirova, vakandikuvadza; Vatariri vamasvingo vakanditorera jasi rangu.
\p
\v 8 Ndinokupikirai, imi vakunda veJerusaremu,
\s Kana mukawana mudiwa wangu,
