\v 1 C
\v 1 .\‘‘. M"\l'IMJ Wfa l'
\v 101110
\p
\v 9 Ko mudiwa wako anopfuura vamwe vadiwa neiko,
\s Nhai, iwe, unopfuura vakadzi vose nokunaka?
\s Ko mudiwa wako unopfuura
\s vamwe vadiwa neiko,
\s Zvaunotipikira saizvozvo?
\s loMudiwa wangu akachena
\s nokutsvuka,
\s Anozikanwa pakati pezana ramazana.
\s "Musoro wake wakaita sendarama yakaisvonaka;
\s Vhudzi rake rakapetana, idema segunguo.
\p
\v 12 Meso ake akaita seenjiva pahova dzemvura,
\s Dzakashambwa nomukaka, sezvibwe
\s zvakarongedzwa zvakanaka. Matarna ake akaita sendima yemiti inonhuwira,
\s Samatutu emiriwo inonaka; Miromo yake yakaita samaruva anodonha mura inoyerera.
\p
\v 14 Maoko ake akaita samapango endarama, akaiswa bheriri; Muviri wake wakaita senyanga dzenzou, dzakafukidzwa nesafiro.
\p
\v 15 Makumbo ake akaita sembiru dzamabwe machena, dzakaiswa pazvigadziko zvendarama
\s yakaisvonaka;
\s Kuonekwa kwake kwose
\s kwakafanana neRebhanoni, kwakaisvonaka semisidhari.
\p
\v 16 Muromo wake wakanaka kwazvo; Zvirokwazvo, wakaisvonaka
\s kwazvo-kwazvo.
\s Ndizvo zvakaita mudiwa wangu, ndizvo zvakaita shamwari yangu, Imi vakunda veJerusaremu.
